OL,3,CGive people with certain conditions
OL,4,Cannual BMI checks, draft guidance
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,FPeople with certain long-term health
OL,8,Fconditions should have their weight
OL,9,Fchecked once a year to allow doctors
OL,10,Fto pinpoint those at risk of
OL,11,Fcomplications like diabetes or heart
OL,12,Fdisease, the National Institute for
OL,13,FHealth and Care Excellence (NICE) has
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FThe new draft guidance could cover
OL,17,Fpatients with the likes of rheumatoid
OL,18,Farthritis, learning disabilities and
OL,19,Fobstructive sleep apnoea, as well as
OL,20,Fheart failure and stroke.
