OL,4,Cannual BMI checks, draft guidance
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,FWhile patients with long-term
OL,8,Fconditions already have annual health
OL,9,Fchecks, body mass index (BMI) or waist-
OL,10,Fto-height ratio is not always
OL,11,Frecorded, according to NICE.
OL,13,FWhile the document does not give a
OL,14,Fdefinitive list of conditions, it
OL,15,Fsuggests doctors should focus on
OL,16,Fpatients with:
OL,18,FHeart failure
OL,20,FLearning disabilities
