OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,FIt also suggests there should be
OL,8,Fannual follow-ups for those discharged
OL,9,Ffrom bariatric surgery services, as
OL,10,Fwell as support for people with
OL,11,Flearning disabilities to access weight
OL,12,Fmanagement services.
OL,14,F"These simple annual measurements
OL,15,Fcreate opportunities for early
OL,16,Fintervention and conversations about
OL,17,Flong-term health and wellbeing," said
OL,18,FProfessor Jonathan Benger, Deputy
OL,19,FChief Executive and Chief Medical
OL,20,FOfficer at NICE.
