OL,3,CGive people with certain conditions
OL,4,Cannual BMI checks, draft guidance
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,F"Annual monitoring of BMI and waist-to-
OL,8,Fheight ratio is a powerful tool to
OL,9,Fhelp prevent problems developing such
OL,10,Fas the onset of diabetes, heart
OL,11,Fdisease or other obesity-related
OL,12,Fconditions.
OL,14,F"Once implemented, these proposed
OL,15,Fquality standards could significantly
OL,16,Fimprove health outcomes for people
OL,17,Fwith long-term conditions by ensuring
OL,18,Fconsistent, timely support for weight
OL,19,Fmanagement across all healthcare
OL,20,Fsettings." He added.
