OL,4,Cannual BMI checks, draft guidance
OL,5,Csuggests
OL,7,FThe draft quality standard is open for
OL,8,Fpublic consultation until April 15.
OL,10,FThe final guidance is expected to be
OL,11,Fpublished in August.
OL,13,FDr Rebecca Payne, GP and chair of the
OL,14,Fquality standards advisory committee,
OL,15,Fadded: "We want to hear from
OL,16,Fhealthcare professionals and
OL,17,Fcommissioners during the consultation
OL,18,Fperiod to understand whether the
OL,19,Fproposals we have made can be
OL,20,Fimplemented in the NHS.
